column2: Ian: Aber hey, wegen dem was da vorhin in der Bar passiert ist. Danke nochmal. Der Typ hatte echt zu viel gebechert.
column3: Ian: But hey, because of what happened in the bar earlier. Thanks again. The guy really had been drinking too much.

column2: Robert: Ach, nicht der Rede wert.
Ian: Werde es dir trotzdem nicht vergessen.
Robert: Kann doch andersherum dasselbe erwarten?
column3: Robert: I could expect the same thing from you, right?

column2: Robert: Egal was deine Mom über mich erzählt?
column3: Robert: No matter what your mom is saying about me?
